{
  "stem": "2581.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Immediately, these planes swarmed down on that spot, and they started throwing bombs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at that time, there were 39 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some were killed, some were, you know, injured, very seriously.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because I remember my father was working on them under the-- by the pump, because we were washing them up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was all so primitive at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everyone was completely unprepared for this situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- This is-- this is how it started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was within a week's time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when they come-- came to-- before they came to town, I and my father ran away from town, thinking that we will run away from the Germans, because we were men.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were afraid they were going to hurt us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So by the time we walked to the next town, which was 18 kilometers, like 12 miles, they were already there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we walked back, we saw dead people lined up, you know, in the- in the ditches and along the road.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when we came to the house-- to the house, my mother somehow expected that we were coming back, because she had prepared for us a Shabbat meal.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a Friday.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the first anti-Jewish-- it was really at first, it started with the intelligentsia of the town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would take the teachers, the priests, the rabbi-- any people that the [NON-ENGLISH] in town, that the Volksdeutschen would tell them, that were patriots, Polish patriots.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were some Jewish people that were very dedicated Polish citizens, so they took everyone up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't exactly Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They took out people in the marketplace and they gave them brooms to sweep the dirt and the mud.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is something like you're pushing water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There's dirt in the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There's dirt on-- on-- on the cobblestone.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
